[I] Five-in-a-row Board Game

[T] Bovo is a Gomoku like game for two players, where the opponents alternate
[T] in placing their respective pictogram on the game board. (Also known as:
[T] Connect Five, Five in a row, X and O, Naughts and Crosses)

[U] https://apps.kde.org/bovo/

